  About XIAWAO   Since 2010, we have been specializing in the design and manufacture of consumer electronics products. Each product is carefully designed and continuously improved and upgraded with the feedback from consumers' experience, always pursuing the best user experience and the best after-sales service.  


 XIAWAO USB to USB C Cable   ✔ Stress Relief Design   ✔ Brand New Exterior Design   ✔ High Quality Connectors  
    The stress relief design using TPE high elasticity material firmly connects the cable to the tip, greatly improving the durability of the cable. title: USB Multi Plug Outlet Extender - YISHU Surge Protector with Rotating Plug, 6 AC Plug Extender with 3 USB Ports, 3-Sided Swivel Power Strip Best Ideal Stocking Stuffers for Adults
availability: This item cannot be shipped to your selected delivery location. Please choose a different delivery location.
description:
Product description  





 YISHU USB Multi Plug Outlet Extender with 90 degree rotating AC plug, 6 AC Outlets and 3 USB Ports    6 STANDARD AC OUTLETS   - 6 AC outlets surge protector with standard 1.5 inches in between, Can be used for a variety of devices.   2 USB A & 1 USB C SMART CHARGING PORTS   - 3 USB ports total 3.4 A, Each USB A port features 5V/2.4A Max output. USB C charging port features 5V/3A MAX.   - NOTE: The UCB-C port is not Quick Charger 3.0, doesn't support any other devices which need 9~22V charging voltage.   90 DEGREE ROTATING AC PLUG   - the rotating AC plug can turn left and right 90 degrees conveniently, to facilitate the use of the device in different directions.   SURGE PROTECTION LED INDICATOR   - The indicator can effectively understand whether the product is in the state of surge protection when used.  






 
 



  Specifications:      Input Voltage: 100-240VAC; 60HZ     Max.Current: 15A     Max.Power Rating: 1875W     Surge Protection Rating: 900 Joules     USB Port Output: DC 5V, Total 3.4A     


 USB Multi Plug Outlet Extender,the rotating AC plug can turn left and right 90 degrees conveniently   900 Joules Power Strip Surge Protector With 6 Outlets And 3 USB Charging Ports   2USB A Charging Ports and 1USB C Charging Port (total output DC 5V/3.4A), Each USB A port features 5V/2.4A Max output. USB C charging port features 5V/3A MAX. Built in smart technology, detecting charging devices and deliver optimal charging speed automatically, compatible with Kindle and most USB devices.   The rotatable AC plug with 6 standard plugs(900 Joules) can be easily rotated 90 degrees left and right to be used wherever needed.  
    6 AC Outlet Splitter     2 USB A & 1 USB C Smart Charging Ports     Surge Protection LED Indicator     turn left and right 90 degree rotating AC plug     Item Dimensions: 5.2*2.03*1.9 inches     











 
 9 IN 1 Multi Plug Outlet   6 AC Outlet Splitter with built-in surge protector (900 Joules) and 2 USB A Charging Ports & 1 USB C Charging Port (total output DC 5V/3.4A), 90 degree rotating AC plug.  


 
 USB-C Charging Port   USB C charging port features 5V/3A MAX.   It can charge your devices that need to use the USB C port.  


 
 6 Standard Plugs   6 standard plugs built-in surge protector (900 Joules), Unique 3-sided design, each direction with two AC Outlets, so you can use your device in different directions at the same time.  


 
 Unique 3 Side Design Power Strip   Unique 3 Side Design Power Strip with 6 AC Outlets, Use 3 large adapters or 6 standard plugs. the rotating AC plug can turn left and right 90 degrees conveniently, use anywhere needed.  









 
 Surge protection LED indicator   Surge protection LED indicator: The indicator can effectively understand whether the product is in the state of surge protection when used.   Tip: If the surge protection LED does not light up, please do not use it for a while and check the cause.  


 
 900 Joules Surge Protection   This USB Multi Plug Outlet Extender comes with a surge protector, minimum energy-absorbing capacity of 900 Joules, Can provide some protection for your equipment from voltage fluctuations, surges, and spikes.   Tip: If you need professional protection for your expensive equipment, we recommend that you purchase a professional protector.  


 
 1382°F Flame-Retardant Materials Shell   1382 ° F flame retardant material housing can effectively prevent the occurrence of fire, to ensure the safety.   Tips: For your safety, do not exceed the product's power rating of 1875W when using the device, otherwise it may cause damage to your device!  


 
 Compact and easy to carry   Our products are compact and lightweight, only the size of a cell phone. This is a great convenience to carry, and is an excellent choice for your travel.

title: GE 6-Outlet Surge Protector, 8 Ft Extension Cord, Power Strip, 1300 Joules, Flat Plug, Twist-to-Close Safety Covers, Protected Indicator Light, ETL Listed, Black, 33662
description: Experience expanded power with the GE-branded 6-Outlet Surge Protector. Featuring six grounded outlets with 1,300 Joules of surge protection, this surge protector transforms your regular outlet into a versatile, efficient powering station. The dynamic 8ft. range of this surge protector makes it a must-have when you need power and protection from a distance. This heavy-duty cord is strong enough to last a lifetime but pliable enough to easily fully extend. The integrated circuit breaker intuitively shuts off power to the unit when voltage spikes or overheating occur. The protected indicator light provides at-a-glance verification that your electronics are safe and properly powered.Included keyhole slots on this extension cord make it a breeze to mount to a wall, desk, workbench or counter. Twist-to-close safety covers securely cover open outlets to restrict their usage and prevent the insertion of foreign objects, eliminating potential electrical hazards to you and your family. The space-saving design of the flat plug is engineered to allow the power cord to sit close to the wall. Get the most from your outlet with the GE-branded 6-Outlet Surge Protector.

 What if my iPhone/Apple Watch/AirPods heat up during charging?  


 It may warm up slightly while using this charging station for Apple devices. To prevent overheating:   1.Avoid using protective case thicker than 2 mm.   2.Keep metal accessories, credit cards or pop sockets away from the wireless charger 3 in 1.  



 Why is the charging slow on my iPhone and Watch Charging Station?  


 For chargers for multiple devices:   1.It normally takes 3-4 hours to fully charge devices through the charging pad.   2.Ensure no metal objects block the Apple charging station, as they can cause high temperatures and slow charging.  



 What if my Phone is not Charging on phone chargers?  


 1.Confirm your phone supports wireless charging.   2.Check that the case is not too thick and remove any metal or uneven objects.   3.Adjust the phone to the correct charging position.   4.Unplug and replug the charging adapter after a few seconds.  



 What if my AirPods is not charging on this Apple 3 in 1 charging station?  


 1.Confirm your Airpods supports wireless charging.   2.AirPods 3rd gen or AirPods Pro with MagSafe cases are compatible.   3.AirPods 4 with ANC supports wireless charging.   P.S.1st/2nd/3rd gen AirPods with Lightning cases are not compatible.  



 My Apple Watch won’t charge on the Apple Watch Charger Stand.  


 1.Reset the charger station by unplugging/replugging.   2.Update watch software through the Watch app on the Phone> General > Software Update.

title: 2025 Upgrade: Longer Size for 5 Fingers,Visible Pure Silver & Carbon Fiber Professional Finger Sleeves for Mobile Gaming–No Rubber Band, Maximum Touch Sensitivity, Anti-Sweat,10 Pack (M)
description:
Product description  




 



  2025 NEW Longer Finger Sleeve   We have added an extra 2 cm in length to the standard size to ensure a perfect fit for all  5 fingers. When worn, it can cover over 90% of the fingers as much as possible, which resolves issues of slipping and looseness.   Nuozme replaces the regular tight elastic band at the bottom with a stretchy carbon fiber piece that spreads pressure evenly, ensuring a comfortable fit and allowing for long wear without leaving marks on your fingers.   The responsive part is woven from visible pure silver fibers, ensuring high sensitivity and addressing issues of sluggish response.   .
features_text: High Quality Pure Silver Fiber - The reactive part is woven with visible pure silver fiber, and each yarn possesses excellent conductivity, approaching the limit of conductivity. It enables easy transmission of static electricity from the fingertips to smartphones, with high sensitivity even during continuous tapping (Common silver finger sleeves are made with a mixture of conductive fibers and non-conductive yarn in the reactive part) | Optimized Design& Comfortable to Wear The Professional Finger Sleeves combine pure silver fiber and carbon fiber for high sensitivity and comfort. Nuozme Finger Sleeves Replace the traditional rubber band at the bottom with a single piece of highly elastic yet comfortable carbon fiber that evenly distributes pressure across the finger. This design helps relieve finger pain and keeps the sleeves securely in place | High Sensitivity & Residue Resistance The finger sleeves have excellent absorption and drying properties, quickly absorbing sweat to maintain comfort. The touch area is made of pure silver fiber, which provides outstanding conductivity, ensuring smooth on-screen movements without delay. This makes them ideal for shooting games, sound-based games, and more | Longer Version: Based on buyer feedback that the regular size slips off easily, we added an extra 2 cm in length for a better fit for all five fingers. Nuozme elastic finger sleeves are adjustable. one size fits all five fingers. They are suitable for all touchscreen devices.Use our extended version, and you no longer have to worry about slipping off | 【PACKAGE INCLUDE】10 pack 【MATERIAL】High-Quality Pure Silver Fiber( in the reactive part)+Carbon Fiber(at the bottom) 【WARM TIPS】1: Size M fits most people. description: Movo CRC01 Waterproof Nylon Rain Cover The Movo CRC01 rain cover protects your camera and lenses from the worst the weather has to offer without stopping you from getting great photos. Rain, snow, sand, and windblown grit are unavoidable on some assignments. Proper preparation is essential for protecting your valuable gear and ensuring the best photos. - prepare yourself with this high-quality nylon rain cover. Certified waterproof material ensures that no precipitation penetrates the camera space, while the large window panel on the back of the rain cover gives you an unobscured look at your camera settings and controls. Two adjustable, cinching sleeves allow you get to your camera without exposing the contents to the elements, and a cinch band locks the cover into place around your lens - allowing you to stay composed in the face of inclement and changing weather conditions.

title: SureCall Flare 3.0 Cell Phone Signal Booster for Home & Office up to 3500 sq ft, Boosts 5G/4G LTE, Yagi Outdoor Antenna, Multi-User, Verizon AT&T Sprint T-Mobile, FCC Approved, USA Company
availability: This item cannot be shipped to your selected delivery location. Please choose a different delivery location.
description: Boost your cell signal in your home with the SureCall Flare 3.0 The SureCall Flare 3.0 4G booster kit is an easy-to-use cell phone signal booster for home. It boosts 4G, LTE, and 3G signal speed for all carriers and phones. Bundled with a powerful yagi directional antenna, you get an extra 9 dB of gain compared to the normal Flare. The Surecall Flare 3.0 cellular signal booster combines the booster and indoor antenna to streamline the system's design for easier installation and an attractive, low-profile appearance. The stylish one-piece base unit is designed to be placed on an open tabletop or shelf for clearer and more reliable voice and data performance. The two pieces are connected via the included 50ft premium RG-6 coaxial cable. Kit includes a yagi directional antenna that reaches distant cell towers. The Flare 3.0 4G signal booster uses a yagi directional antenna to provide more gain to your amplifier. With strong outside signal, you can expect up to 3,000 sq ft of indoor coverage. With weaker outside signal, that coverage may decrease to around 1500 sq ft. The Surecall Flare 3.0 cell phone signal repeater works with all carriers in the United States and Canada: AT&T, T-Mobile, Verizon, Sprint, Straight Talk, Trackphone and U.S. Cellular. Get your Flare 3.0 cellular booster today for the most stylish, simplest solution to solve your poor signal issues.
features_text: PRODUCT FEATURES— The SureCall Flare 3.0 cell phone signal amplifier boosts weak signal in 2-4 rooms, up to 3500 sq ft inside any home or office. This results in fewer dropped calls, improved battery life, higher audio quality, and faster data and streaming for AT&T, T-Mobile, Verizon, Sprint, Straight Talk, U.S. Cellular and many more. Flare 3.0 boosts 5G/4G LTE voice, text and data signals for all North American cell carriers, including Verizon’s 5G Nationwide data signals..Maximum Gain: 72 dB | COVERAGE AREA— The indoor coverage area that the Flare 3.0 creates varies based on existing signal at the exterior antenna location: 1-2 bars outside ~ 1500 sq ft inside, 3-4 bars ~ 2500 sq ft, 5 bars ~ 3500 sq ft. If there is weak signal where the exterior antenna is installed, we recommend a booster kit that includes components to capture and broadcast a stronger signal, like the Fusion4Home Max. If there is no available signal to boost at the exterior antenna location, a signal booster will not work. | BEST PERFORMANCE— Finding a location with consistent signal that the Yagi antenna can capture is important and will improve performance. Indoor coverage area is directly related to the existing signal strength available at the exterior antenna location. For best performance we recommend a minimum 30 feet of horizontal separation between the base station and exterior antenna. Without this separation performance will suffer and the coverage area will be reduced. 2XP technology delivers 2x uplink power for best performance in remote areas | EASY INSTALL— Simply set up the Yagi outdoor antenna, run the cable into your home, and place the cellular amplifier (base unit) where you want. Other boosters require you to run cables or drill holes to install the indoor antenna, but not the Flare 3.0 - it has the indoor antenna integrated to the amplifier. Resembling a speaker, Flare 3.0 fits right in to any modern room living room, bedroom, or office. Place It wherever in your building you need improved cellular signal and the amplifier will automatically boost your signal. | BUILT TO LAST— Designed and tested in the USA with the high-quality components for longevity and connectivity where you need it most. Includes industry best 3-year warranty and lifetime US-based tech support. FCC approved signal boosters. SureCall is proudly American owned and operated– US company based in Silicon Valley California. SureCall is an Authorized Verizon 5G Signal Booster Vendor.

title: JOYTUTUS Shower Phone Holder, Reusable Suction Cup Phone Mount for Shower, Mirror, Kitchen, Window & Bathroom, Shower Phone Mount Compatible with iPhone 16, 15, 14, 13, 12 & All Phones
description: Product description
features_text: EVERYDAY CELL PHONE HOLDER：The suction cup phone mount is ideal for taking selfies, creating vlogs or makeup tutorials, watching movies in the bathroom, or cooking videos in the kitchen. Simply use one hand to press the button to install the mirror phone holder | EASY TO USE :The suction cups work on a variety of smooth surfaces, including mirrors, plastic, acrylic, glass, metal, tile, and marble. The MagSafe suction mount can be easily installed on mirrors, shower walls, and kitchen and gym walls, freeing up your hands for selfies, makeup, watching videos, and cooking | SUPER STRONG MAGNETIC FORCE：Don't worry about dropping your phone; the magnet can securely hold it so that it may be laid either horizontally or vertically. It can hold up to 3.31 pounds. Fits for iPhone 16, 15, 14, 13, and 12 series and MagSafe cases; for other phones and non-magnetic security cases, you need to attach the included magnetic metal ring to the back of the phone case . (Not compatible with Galaxy S21） | FLEXIBLE ADJUSTMENT & PORTABLE：The suction phone mount can be folded and is very small, making it easy to carry in your backpack or luggage. We designed the telescopic pole and 180° rotating axis to give you the most flexible view angle possible, allowing you to freely adjust the shooting angle and get a better picture | REUSABLE SUCTION CUPS：You can remove the MagSafe wall mount by pressing the button with one hand. The vacuum adsorption adhesive pad is reusable and will not leave any unsightly marks when removed. If the suction disappears, please clean and reuse it | PRO TIPS FOR A STRONGER HOLD ON TEXTURED SURFACES: If you're mounting on grainy, uneven, or textured surfaces (like dashboards), use the included pc pad for a strong suction:1. clean the surface and peel off the pad's protective film.2. press the pad firmly onto the mounting area.3. attach the suction cup to the center of the pad and lock it.The pad creates a smooth base, ensuring a rock-solid grip by allowing full air expulsion!

 Previous page    


 

 The Gear You Need for the Life You Lead.   We always explore new ways to make people’s lives simpler, safer, richer, and happier. That’s why we build the accessories that power your phone, use it hands-free while you drive, listen to great music anywhere, monitor your heart rate, film your ATV ride, jump start your truck, and more. So you can focus on following your passions.  



  


 

 Scosche was founded in 1980 as a car audio consulting business by Roger and Scotia Alves. Today, with 200 employees, we've expanded to offer over 4,000 consumer technology, power sports, and car audio products. We remain a family-owned company with three generations of the Alves family at our California headquarters, upholding our commitment to innovation, quality, safety, and value.  



  



 Scosche Mission Statement   Our goal: Innovative, affordable accessories, top service, and great customer experience through American ingenuity.  

 Our "Why"   Scosche was born from, and runs on our passion for cool vehicles, amazing sounds, the great outdoors, travel, motorsports, horsepower and voltage. We’re a company of gearheads, drivers, surfers, racers, riders, tech buffs, tech users, innovators, and relentless pursuers of perfection.  

 Follow Your Dreams   Wherever they may take you. Just remember to take your Scosche Accessories for Life along for the ride!  




  


 

 Reforestation and GHGs   We reduce GHGs by using 100% renewable energy and have partnered with Eden Reforestation, an organization that works to restore landscapes around the world. features_text: 4-in-1 Car Video Box: Enjoy a seamless wireless experience with this Wireless CarPlay Adapter, android auto wireless adapter, and Android 12.0 system – all in one device. Easily transform your driving journey into an entertainment hub by streaming your favorite content directly to your car's display | Download More Apps Freely: Pre-installed with Netflix, YouTube, and more, you can stream your favorite content directly on your car screen without additional devices. Plus, you can easily download more apps from Google Play & App Store, customizing your in-car entertainment experience to make every trip more enjoyable | Compatibility Alert: Your vehicle must already have wired CarPlay or Android Auto for the AI Box to function. Compatible with iPhone 7+/iOS 10.0+ and Android 11.0+. Includes USB-A to Type-C & Type-C to Type-C cables for broad adaptability. (Note: Not compatible with Te-sla/B-M-W.) | Powerful Streaming Device: Experience fast and smooth performance with a Quad-core 2.0 GHz ARM Cortex-A53 processor, 4GB RAM+32GB storage, and Bluetooth 5.1 & 5.0, ensuring a powerful and stable connection | Dual-Band WiFi: Equipped with 2.4G & 5G dual-band WiFi, ensuring that CarPlay & Android Auto and streaming apps can run simultaneously without frequent reconnections, making your driving experience smoother and more enjoyable | Smart Split-Screen & Phone Mirroring: Supports split-screen mode, allowing you to navigate while watching videos for added convenience. It also features screen mirroring, enabling you to cast your smartphone screen onto the car’s display for easy sharing of photos, videos, and social media content | HDMI Output & USB: Comes with an HDMI output port, allowing you to cast videos to rear-seat entertainment screens or TVs, making it perfect for family trips or long drives. Supports USB media playback, so you can enjoy locally stored videos and music even in areas with poor internet connectivity | Remote Control Included: Comes with a remote control, allowing you to easily control all functions, whether your vehicle has a touchscreen or not, for a convenient and effortless user experience

description: Instructions:1. Clean the watch glass and calendar crystal.2. Coat the bottom of the calendar crystal with shadowless adhesive (ultraviolet adhesive). It should not be applied too thickly. Place the calendar crystal grain above the position of the watch glass on the watch calendar display to a good position.3. If the position is not right, do not use the purple light (ultraviolet light) first, you can adjust the position of the calendar crystal, if there is excess adhesive overflow, wipe it off in time.4. After confirming that the calendar crystal is placed in the correct position and no adhesive overflows, irradiate it with a purple light (ultraviolet light) for about 15 seconds.5. The adhesive is solidified and the installation is complete.Precautions:The above reference step uses UV shadowless adhesive (ultraviolet adhesive), which is transparent and traceless after drying.If the position of the calendar crystal is wrong, don't light up! Before illumination, it can be adjusted at will, and the adhesive is non-sticky. After lighting the lamp, the adhesive will solidify and cannot be adjusted! If the glue overflows, you can wipe it off before illumination. It will solidify after been illuminated. You can only scrape off the overflowed adhesive bit by bit with a cutter or wipe it off with alcohol.Package includes:1*Calendar lens(The lens installation requires ultraviolet adhesive which is not included)

 Larger spacing Outlet   The AC outlets with 1.78 inches long space in between, larger than standard 1.5-inch socket. Larger spacing makes it easier to use for all kinds of equipment.  


 
 45° plug design is more convenient to use   The 45° plug design makes it possible not to interfere with your simultaneous use of other devices, which brings the best experience.  









 
 Multi Safety Protection   The surge protector with overload protection protects your electrical appliances from lighting, surges or spikes. The minimum energy-absorbing capacity of 600 Joules. It will automatically cut power to protect connected devices when voltage surge is overwhelming.  


 
 1382°F Flame-Retardant Materials Shell   1382 ° F flame retardant material housing can effectively prevent the occurrence of fire, to ensure the safety, tips.  6 Ft Extension Cord with Cable Tie   6 Feet Right Angled Flat Plug power cord makes it more flexible ,Reusable Fastening Cable Ties Can tie up the unused cord and make it better organized.  


 
 Mounting Hole   Mounting Method   1. Measure the distance between the 2 keyhole slots with the same direction on the back of the power strip.   2. Please ensure that the screws slide into the smaller holes.

title: Variable Extension Telescope Camera Adapter - for Canon SLR Cameras Connected to Telescopes - for Prime- Focus Or Eyepiece-Projection Photography
description:
Product description  




   

   Starboosa Variable Extension Telescope Camera Adapter   Essential accessory for anyone interested in astrophotography.Suitable for all Canon SLR cameras for prime focus or eyepiece projection photography.Extension tube can accommodate eyepieces up to 38mm (1.49 ").After connecting the eyepieces, the distance between the  front and rear can be adjusted to zoom in or out to obtain a zoomable  image.It is recommended to use eyepieces, which can be fixed in the barrel, so the camera can get higher quality images.Tips:  Mirrorless cameras are not suitable for use.(Choose: Full-Frame mirrorless camera adapter. Search its ASIN:B08LYP5YST)

 Type 3   Combination order:   SLR +T-ring+1.25"T adapter +telescope

features_text: 【Professional Wireless Lavalier Mic Set for Camera】 NEEWER CM28 is a mini Wireless Clip on Lapel Microphone kit with 2 transmitters (TX) and 1 receiver (RX). They can operate for 9 hours (TX) and 8 hours (RX) once fully charged, ideal devices for outdoor audio & video recording, stage, vlogging, podcasting, interview, and live streaming. Charge them twice in just 1.5 hours each time with the included protective charging case. | 【Standalone Recording Accessories】 The TXs double as recording pens with each 4GB storage, saving up to 9 hours of uncompressed 48KHz WAV audio files. 3 audio export modes: Mono, Stereo, and Ms. Support one tap decibel (dB) gain. An LCD screen displays modes, volume, battery levels, connection status, noise reduction, etc. These small wireless lav mics are portable essentials as a starter tool kit for TikTok, YouTube, and other social media content creators, influencers | 【One Click Noise Canceling & Recording】 The advanced noise canceling chip built into the small cordless microphones allows you to achieve clear and crisp voice recording at one click of the same button. Two LED indicators for showing different recording statuses. These handheld microphones come with two windshields for noise reduction and magnets for fixing the professional lavalier mics magnetically on the collars, shirt pocket or elsewhere | 【656ft/200m Constant Transmission】 In unobstructed areas, CM28 ensures a 656ft (200m) of smooth wireless transmission for stable audio recording and higher resistance against interference. Note: The transmission range varies on locations | 【Widely Compatible RX Receiver】 The little external micro phone for phone video recording is compatible with iPhone 16 15 Pro Max Plus 14 13 12 11 Samsung Galaxy S24 S23 Ultra Andriod cell phones with the included Type C OTG adapter accessories. Also includes a white USB A to Type C data cable for PC MAC computer transmission (note that the black one is only for charging), and a camera audio cable for connecting DSLR cameras

description: The Voyager Legend earpiece headset delivers unsurpassed audio clarity, all-day comfort, and the hands-free mobility you need to take calls on the road or on the go. Sound the way you want with your Plantronics headset’s triple-mic active Digital Signal Processing (DSP), with noise and wind canceling—the perfect remedy for blocking out distracting background sound. With its Bluetooth connection, the Voyager Legend lets you freely move up to 33 feet (10 meters) as well as connect a second smartphone or tablet with your headset’s multipoint technology. Smart sensors take a load off your shoulders by pausing your music and routing calls directly to your mobile. Voice commands further simplify how you communicate by letting you answer or ignore calls, check battery level, and monitor connection status by merely tapping the voice command button and then speaking. Plus, the mute, volume, and power buttons are located on your headset for easy access. The Voyager Legend also sports a balanced and comfortable design—you’ll practically forget you’re wearing it! The convenience continues thanks to the included charging cord’s magnetic, snap-fit connection making recharging your phone headset quick and easy.

features_text: [Award Honored, Full Audio] FIFINE AmpliGame A6V, a gaming mic, has earned the globally recognized iF Design Award. The PC microphone with 192kHz sampling rate delivers naturally detailed audio, making your team sound like they're right beside you. Cardioid polar pattern and 70dB SNR offer dual support for pure voice, sensitive to the front vocal and reducing background noise interference. The streaming mic helps you win more easily. | [Quick Mute Button, Handy Gain Knob] Immediately silence the USB microphone with a tap, preventing emotional outbursts to maintain a positive team atmosphere. RGB off when muted to indicate status and prevent streaming accidents. Mic volume control conveniently located on the condenser microphone is intuitive to use. You can speak at a comfortable level without shouting or whispering during game. | [Gradient RGB] Bicolored RGB cycles through 7 gradient colors automatically. Vivid lighting on the FIFINE microphone for PC enhances your glowing rig for a carnival atmosphere, immersing you in the intense game arena. The computer microphone for desktop with fixed light modes achieves a personalized experience without visual clutter, randomly matching game characters for surprise color combos. | [Plug and Play] The PS5 microphone is easy to install and compatible with PS4, desktop, laptop and mainstream operating systems like Windows/Mac OS, without extra software. Quickly start game chat on Discord, Team and Zoom, or stream on OBS, Streamlabs and Twitch platforms. The gaming microphone PC coming with 6.6ft-long detachable USB cable ensures no interruptions or connectivity issues, even if your computer host is under the desk. | [Useful Accessories] The podcast microphone features durable construction. Anti-vibration shock mount with four rubber bands absorbs tremor from keyboard taps and mouse clicks. The detachable pop filter reduces plosives caused by excited speech during gaming. The stable tripod stand with rubber feet allows for optimal recording positioning via an adjustable thumbscrew, whether you're leaning back or in. | [Product Includes] The studio microphone comes with Shock Mount and Pop Filter*1, Tripod Stand*1, 6.6 feet USB Cable*1, User's Manual*1

title: DJI Osmo Mobile 6 Gimbal Stabilizer for Smartphones, 3-Axis Phone Gimbal, Built-In Extension Rod, Object Tracking, Portable and Foldable, Vlogging Stabilizer, YouTube TikTok, Slate Gray
description: Overview This intelligent gimbal is lightweight and compact. Simply unfold to start filming smooth dynamic footage. With the built-in extension rod, you can include more friends in the photo and take the perfect selfie. A whole host of intelligent features are at your fingertips, including ShotGuides to help capture the scenario you're in or creative features like Timelapse. Use the DJI Mimo to add the final touches to your content and share. DJI Osmo Mobile 6 is the ultimate creative tool to elevate your creations on the go.  Features A new status display panel: Check how much battery you have left, system indicator status, or which gimbal mode you're in. The M button makes it easy to switch between different modes and get unique with your shots.  Flip between horizontal and vertical: It's as effortless as double-clicking the switch button to go from horizontal to vertical shooting.  Notes 1. Auto pop-ups on the DJI Mimo app are only supported on iPhone and are subject to actual circumstances. When using DJI Osmo Mobile 6 for the first time, enable Quick Launch in the DJI Mimo app and follow the instructions to complete authorization.  2. Tested when following a single subject.  3. LightCut is a smartphone editing app recommended by DJI. 4. Currently, only Apple Watch is supported (Apple Watch Series 7/8/9, Apple Watch SE 2, Apple Watch Ultra 1/2, with an operating system of watchOS 9 or later).* Due to platform compatibility issue, the DJI Mimo app has been removed from Google Play. You cannot search for DJI Mimo in Google Play. To ensure a better product usage experience, please log in to the DJI official website to download the latest version of DJI Mimo.
features_text: Stay on Point with ActiveTrack 6.0 - With upgraded tracking tech, OM 6 sticks to your energetic kids or playful pets like glue. You can even make it track yourself. Become the star of your own film without needing anyone's help. | Remote Control With Watch - Install the DJI Mimo app on your Apple Watch, and turn it into a smart remote for Osmo Mobile 6. Remotely view camera feeds, adjust the gimbal's angle, and capture photos and record videos all from your watch. | Silky Smooth Shots with 3-Axis Stabilization - You know what ruins videos? Shaky footage. DJI OM 6 is here to help. This phone gimbal ensures super steady shots, even when you're on the move. Say hello to buttery-smooth videos. | So quick, So easy - This smartphone stabilizer powers on as soon as you unfold it. Just attach your phone, and you are ready to shoot. Catch that breathtaking sunset or your child's smile without missing a beat. | Lightweight, Compact, and Extendable - With a foldable design and weighing only 305g, this cell phone gimbal stabilizer is easy to take anywhere. Extend the built-in extension rod to get creative angles or the perfect selfie. | Shoot Like a Pro, Even If You're a Newbie - OM 6's ShotGuides recognizes your scene and suggests a shot sequence. From romantic outings to picnics, follow the steps to easily create stunning films, even if it's your first time. | Use Side Wheel to Get Cinematic Effects - The side wheel gives you power over focus and zoom. Nail that cinematic blur or try a Hitchcock zoom for some dramatic flair. Up your video game and impress your friends with high-quality videos. | The gimbal is stain resistant and coated in a non-slip texture, with an ergonomic grip that will keep it secure in your hands. It's compatible with most iPhone, Samsung Galaxy, and Huawei series. Please check the compatibility list before purchasing. | New Parents and Kids Mode - Capture and record heartwarming moments with your child as the gimbal autonomously shoots and records, allowing parents to be present in the frame. | Due to platform compatibility issue, the DJI Mimo app has been removed from Google Play. You cannot search for DJI Mimo in Google Play. To ensure a better product usage experience, please log in to the DJI official website to download the latest version of DJI Mimo.

description:
From the brand  











 




 Previous page  


 

 BLEBLE is a professional brand dedicated to offering high-quality iPad styluses. We focus on every detail of the pen’s design, ensuring a comfortable writing experience that closely mimics using a real pencil—without any delay and with exceptional responsiveness, all at a highly affordable price.   BLEBLE strives to provide the best tools to enhance your creativity and productivity on the iPad.  



 



   

   

   

   


 BLEBLE Stylus Pen for Ipad  



 



   

   

   

   


 BLEBLE Stylus Pen for Ipad

features_text: Wide Compatibility with iPad Models - The stylus pencil for ipad is designed to work seamlessly with a range of model for iPad 2018 versions and later (2018-2025), iPad Pen is compatible with iPad 11(A16)/10/9/8/7/6, iPad Air 3/4/5/M2/M3, iPad Pro 11-inch 1/2/3/4/M4, iPad Pro 12.9-inch 3/4/5/6, iPad Pro 13" (M4), iPad Mini 5/6 Gen. Does not compatible with iPhone or Android Phone, Android Tablet, Microsoft devices. Please confirm model compatibility before placing an order. | Precision & Accuracy - This pen stylus is designed for pinpoint precision, making it ideal for detailed tasks like drawing, note-taking, and editing. The tip glides smoothly across the screen, allowing for effortless strokes and lines. Unlike many styluses on the market, ours comes with a durable and stylish storage case, providing extra protection and making it easy to carry wherever you go. | Palm Rejection Technology - Forget about awkward hand positions or unintentional marks on your screen. This pen for ipad features advanced palm rejection, allowing you to rest your hand comfortably on the screen while writing or drawing. The stylus pencil only responds to its tip, ensuring a distraction-free experience, so you can focus on your creative process or productivity without worrying about disrupting your workflow. | Easy to Use No Pairing Needed - With no need for Bluetooth complicated pairing or additional apps, this stylus is truly plug-and-play. title: Flex Slim Flexible Universal Motorcycle Helmet Chin Mount Kit Bendable Silicone Compatible with GoPro Hero 12, 11, 10, DJI Osmo Action, Insta360, SJCAM, Xiaomi Yi Action Cameras (Black)
description:
Product description  




 Benefits of FLEX  


 
 Total Flexibility   The FLEX Slim Chin Mount by MotoRadds is the only helmet mount that is completely flexible. This means that no matter your helmet shape, you can bend and mold the mount exactly to your specifications, making every single mount a custom mount.  


 
 For All Helmets   Originally, MotoRadds was only for motorcycle helmets. Now, with FLEX Slim, this mount is for all helmets. You can use this chin mount on mountain bike helmets, snowmobile helmets, motocross helmets, and so much more. The only caveat is that it's designed for a full face helmet so it can rest on the chin area, but who are we to tell you what to do with it?  


 
 Discreet Placement   The FLEX Slim was designed to be low profile and low key. Designed for chin placement helps keep it close and complementary to your helmet. With a matte black finish and minimal amount of material, your helmet will still look good with or without your camera attached.  


 
 Simplified Mounting Point   We simplified the mounting point so that there's no excessive hardware that's not needed. We kept only what's necessary to mount your camera. This allows you to add any extensions you choose when you're using your camera and to remove as much hardware as possible when you're not.  








 

 Limitless Applications   A chin mount for helmets in every extreme sport.

title: UES FFR24: Full Frame Camera Cleaning Kit 14pcs Sensor Cleaning Swab and 15ml Cleaner Compatible for Sony Nikon Canon FF CCD CMOS Clean
description:
Product description  




   

   Invest in the Best - Choose UES:   Count on the UES FFR24 Full Frame Camera Sensor Cleaning Kit to consistently deliver dependable results, helping you enjoy a seamless photography experience every time you shoot.   With the UES camera cleaning tools, you can trust that your valuable optics will always be in top-notch condition. Capture stunning moments with clear, sharp visuals, thanks to our reliable and easy-to-use camera cleaning tools. Whether you are a professional photographer or an outdoor enthusiast, UES is your go-to solution for maintaining pristine optics.    




 

 Alcohol-Free Sensor Cleaner    UES sensor cleaner is compliant with the EU REACH regulation, and the REACH Certificate of Compliance is issued by SGS.UES sensor cleaner is alcohol-free and ammonia-free.The liquid cleaner is ultrapure water-based with a resistivity of 18.2 MΩ × cm.It is safe for all coatings and can be used for cleaning both CMOS and CCD sensorsIt can effectively remove fingerprints, stains, smudges, and dust on any sensors without leaving a streak behind  








 

  Full-Frame Sensor Cleaning Swabs    UES full-frame sensor cleaning swab is compatible with the camera sensor ≤ 24 mm.UES swab is super soft and flexible. The head of the swab is completely covered with a super fine microfiber cloth. title: S9 Full-Size Gaming Phone Controller for iPhone 15/16, iPad Mini 6/7, Android Tablet, Bluetooth＆Type-C Mobile Gamepad with Free Key Mapping＆App, for Genshin Impact & Zenless Zone Zero, Hall Joystick
description:
Product description  

 
 

 
 
 
   Previous page

   Previous page                Next page   
1 Mobile Gaming 

2 Emulator 

3 Cloud Gaming 

4 Remote Play 
    

    ABXY GAME APP - The most playable gamepad app on the market!   
 Enjoy best-in-class integration for instant access to every gaming system without complicated setups. With comprehensive settings, you can fine-tune every detail, from joystick sensitivity and trigger response to advanced macros, ensuring your controller perfectly matches your playstyle. Plus, take full control with free key mapping, allowing you to remap any button on the fly for peak performance across any game genre. Precision, power, and personalization are all in your hands.

S9 Game Controller Merchant Video

     

   Previous page 
   
 
   
 
   
 
   
Next page   



















      

   Previous page 
         Screenshot Key & Back Buttons     One-click to screenshot your amazing gaming moments! What's more, the back button lets you effortlessly set macros and extra functions—unlock limitless possibilities for your ultimate gaming!       
 
   
 
         Dual Rotor Motors     Equipped with Rotor motor, which is known for it's strong, powerful vibrations, giving that classic Xbox controller feel. In contrast, linear motors can feel stiff and lifeless without proper tuning.       
 
         Hall Effect Joystick and Trigger     S9 features it's Hall effect joysticks and triggers that offer zero drift and zero dead zones, significantly enhancing control precision and ensuring extended durability up to 5 million rotations.       
 
         6-Axis Gyro     Enjoy gyro-assisted aiming for pinpoint precision in FPS games, just like elite controllers. Use the gyro to steer in Forza 5 or to fine-tune your aim in Zelda, adding a whole new layer of control!       
Next page   






















      

   Previous page 
   
 
   
 
   
 
   
 
   
 
   
Next page   

























      

  



 What devices are supported?   


 Most devices with a Type-C port are supported, including most Android phones, iPhone 15 and 16 series, iPad Mini 6 & 7, and Android tablets under 8.8 inches.    



 Can iPhone 14 or earlier models be used?  


 No. The S9 uses a Type-C port, so lightning-port iPhones (iPhone 14 and below) are not supported. Only iPhone 15 and 16 series are compatible.    



 Will the controller block the phone’s camera?  


 The S9 features a recessed design near the camera area. It generally avoids blocking the camera.  



 Can it be used as a PC controller?   


 Yes, but it needs power first—either through a male-to-female charging cable or attaching a small power bank while clamped.  



 Does it support vibration?   


 The controller features small rotary motors for Xbox-style vibration. Note: if the game doesn’t provide vibration data, there will be no feedback.
features_text: [True Full-Size Phone Controller] Unlike other telescopic controllers with small grips, the S9 features a true full-size gamepad design, delivering a console-level controller experience on mobile. | [Handheld-Quality Gaming on Type-C Devices] Fully compatible with iPhone 15/16, iPad Mini 6/7, and Android devices like Samsung, Google Pixel, Motorola, ROG, and Legion. Stretchable up to 216mm, it fits tablets up to 8.8 inches for versatile, uninterrupted gameplay. Does not support foldable phones. | [Play-While-Charging] Supports 5V 1A Quick Charging, allowing uninterrupted gaming in both USB and Bluetooth modes. Play while charging with seamless power passthrough, ensuring your game never gets interrupted. | [Multi-Mode Gaming] Ideal for mobile gaming, emulators, cloud gaming, and remote play. Enjoy handheld-quality control on popular titles like Roblox, Genshin Impact, Call of Duty, and Forza Horizon 5 on your phone or tablet.(On Android devices, playing CODM with the S9 controller requires Bluetooth mode; on Apple devices, you can directly plug in and use.) | [Free abxy Gaming App] Access the most powerful gaming app for mobile controller, supporting local game library, Xbox Cloud Gaming, PS Remote Play, PPSSPP, Delta, and more. Enjoy free key mapping, joystick sensitivity, trigger adjustment, and other features for a fully customized gaming experience. 【The abxy app on iOS is limited: no virtual touch, and local game additions are restricted by Apple's policies, allowing only games from a predefined list—excluding some niche titles】 | [Premium Hardware Features] Equipped with Hall joystick and Hall trigger, dual rotor motors, 6-axis gyro, and programmable back buttons for an unmatched gaming session. | [Ergonomic and Lightweight Design] Weighing just 250g, the S9 fits comfortably even with a phone case. Comes with three D-pad options and two interchangeable joystick heights for versatile control across all game genres. | [Plastic-Free Package] The packaging box, from inside to outside, is made of 100% paper material, so small paper particles inside the box during transport are to be expected. | [With Silicone Spaces] Includes silicone spacers, perfect for using the S9 with bare phones and iPad Mini ensuring the volume buttons or other buttons are not pressed. To ensure 100% compatibility, we recommend using the S9 with tablets less than 213mm in length, and ensure the thickness between the phone case and charging port is under 2mm for S9 compatibility. | Most Android and iOS games lack vibration support. HID mode doesn't support it, while PS, NS, and XInput modes do. On iOS, controllers vibrate if games send signals; on Android, vibration support depends on kernel support for streaming and cloud gaming.

features_text: 【Professional Wireless Lavalier Mic Set for Camera】 NEEWER CM28 is a mini Wireless Clip on Lapel Microphone kit with 2 transmitters (TX) and 1 receiver (RX). They can operate for 9 hours (TX) and 8 hours (RX) once fully charged, ideal devices for outdoor audio & video recording, stage, vlogging, podcasting, interview, and live streaming. Charge them twice in just 1.5 hours each time with the included protective charging case. | 【Standalone Recording Accessories】 The TXs double as recording pens with each 4GB storage, saving up to 9 hours of uncompressed 48KHz WAV audio files. 3 audio export modes: Mono, Stereo, and Ms. Support one tap decibel (dB) gain. An LCD screen displays modes, volume, battery levels, connection status, noise reduction, etc. These small wireless lav mics are portable essentials as a starter tool kit for TikTok, YouTube, and other social media content creators, influencers | 【One Click Noise Canceling & Recording】 The advanced noise canceling chip built into the small cordless microphones allows you to achieve clear and crisp voice recording at one click of the same button. Two LED indicators for showing different recording statuses. These handheld microphones come with two windshields for noise reduction and magnets for fixing the professional lavalier mics magnetically on the collars, shirt pocket or elsewhere | 【656ft/200m Constant Transmission】 In unobstructed areas, CM28 ensures a 656ft (200m) of smooth wireless transmission for stable audio recording and higher resistance against interference. Note: The transmission range varies on locations | 【Widely Compatible RX Receiver】 The little external micro phone for phone video recording is compatible with iPhone 16 15 Pro Max Plus 14 13 12 11 Samsung Galaxy S24 S23 Ultra Andriod cell phones with the included Type C OTG adapter accessories. Also includes a white USB A to Type C data cable for PC MAC computer transmission (note that the black one is only for charging), and a camera audio cable for connecting DSLR cameras

title: TagVault™ AirTag Wallet Holder - The Thinnest AirTag Wallet Card Insert | Flexible, Stays Hidden, Patent Pending | Elevation Lab
description:
Product description  

 
 


 
 
    Wallets are the last thing you want to go missing.   Other Apple AirTag holders are bulky and made from thick hard plastic that stiffens your wallet.   TagVault Wallet is the best way to keep AirTag in your wallet. Ultra-thin, no additional thickness added to AirTag. Flexible silicone construction to conform and flex with your wallet. Shorter than a credit card keeping it hidden. And its shape locks inside credit card slots in your wallet.   Never lose your wallet again.    

  The Worlds Thinnest AirTag Wallet Holder

Flexible Rubber and Fits Great in Wallet
Reviewed in the United States on September 25, 2023Color: 2-PackVerified Purchase


This is a well-made soft rubber housing that is very slim, and exactly fits the Apple Airtag.  It is smaller than a standard credit card size in terms of length and width, but it does fit in the credit Card section of your wallet nicely.  You can easily slip the Airtag into the rubber holder.  Then the rubber holder with the Airtag snuggly fits into a wallet or purse without any issues.  The soft rubber looks like it will hold the position in the Wallet or purse so that it does not fall out, when inserted into the Credit Card slots in the wallet.  It obviously is thicker than a credit card at the position of the Airtag, but the holder itself, does not add significant thickness to the Airtag as the Airtag itself fits into the hole in it.  The holder where the Airtag slips is appears to well-made and sercures the Airtag well.  All in all, a well-made product and I would recommend the Airtag Holder purchase.

Listen, I used to lose my wallet more often than I lose arguments with my wife, which is a lot. It would disappear into couch cushions, jacket pockets, the Bermuda Triangle, you name it. Enter: this glorious little AirTag holder.It slid right into my wallet like it was meant to be there all along, like a taco fits in a Tuesday. Now, when I inevitably “misplace” my wallet (read: forget it on the kitchen counter), I just open the Find My app, tap a button, and BAM, it’s singing a little song like, “Hey dummy, I’m over here!”This thing is sleek, durable, and doesn’t bulk up my wallet like I’m carrying a cheeseburger in my back pocket. If Batman had a wallet, this would be in it.If you’re a fellow human prone to wallet vanishing acts, just get it. Your future self (and your spouse) will thank you.⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️Would give it six stars if it could also remind me where I put my keys.

title: 2 Pack Wireless Lavalier Microphone for iPhone, Professional Lapel Mics, Wireless Mic Plug-Play, Lapel Microphone for Video Recording Interview Vlog YouTube TikTok(for iPhone 14 and Below)
description:
Product description  





 



 



 


   Notes on using steps   1.Please make sure your device is unlocked and the receiver is plugged into the port of your smartphone.   2. Press the power switch of the microphone for about 1 second to turn it on. If the green light for both of receiver and transmitter always keeps on, it means they paired successfully.   3. Press the power switch of the microphone very softly, the green light will keep flashing, which means the recording was paused. By pressing the button again, it will stop flashing and the recording will continue.   4. Any time when you see the red light & green light flashes alternately, it means the connection is failed and you need to restart.   5. Press and hold the power switch for about 3 seconds to power off the microphone.   6. Special note: The receiver does not have a battery inside, and does not need to be charged during live broadcast. If the power of the mobile phone is insufficient during the live broadcast, the mobile phone can be charged directly through the interface of the receiving end.
features_text: 【Lightweight & Clip-on Microphone】The professional lavalier microphone kit has 1 receiver and 2 transmitters included, which makes it possible to record sound or video from both 2 parties at the same time. Also we can use one mic and receiver set according to the occasion. Not compatible with USB-C for iPhone15 and above!The paired data cable is used for microphone-charging,not for the receiver | 【Easy Connection, Plug & Play】The smart clip-on microphone is much easier to use than other microphones. Just plug the receiver into your devices and turn on the power switch of the transmitters, the two parts will get connected successfully and auto paired immediately. Then you can start to record voice or videos without opening extra app or bluetooth in your cellphone.(Note: Bluetooth wireless microphone, if the match is not successful, do not worry, just turn off the device and try again) | 【Omnidirectional Sound & Noise Cancellation】Omnidirectional dual wireless lavalier microphone is built with professional-grade intelligent noise reduction chips, providing effective identification of the original sound and clear recording in noisy environment. Ensure you get quality sound and a better experience | 【65ft Distance & 5H Battery Life】 This portable iPhone microphone is designed with 2.4GHz wireless transmission technology, which helps you get rid of messy wire and cover up to a 65ft stable signal transmission, this mini wireless lavalier microphone provide more than 5 hours of battery life and only 2 hours to get fully charged | 【Compatible with IOS Devices】The wireless tiny microphone is made for iPhone and iPad. Plug the usb microphone receiver into your iOS device to record video anytime. It will be very convenient for you to record on different social media platforms like YouTube, Facebook, Twitter, Tik Tok etc. Bluetooth microphone not available for Android devices unless you have a proper adapter
